snippet.title: The Discriminant of a Quadratic: YOU DON"T NEED IT!
snippet.description: In this video (with a typo in the title!!) I explain how one need not know "b^2-4ac" to answer those dreary algebra questions. AND .. I argue it is more meaningful for students not to know it!! I have opinions!
